	ww.filmfroth.com/oscars) to compete for more prizes! \\nKids and well beha
	ved dogs on leashes are welcome downstairs in the taproom. The loft is 21+
	 and no animals are allowed. Check out Urban Family’s website for more inf
	ormation on their taproom! \\nWe hope to see you there to celebrate anothe
	r amazing year of film with fantastic beer and the great people of Urban F
	amily Brewing!\n\nhttps://myballard.com/event/oscars-watch-party/\n\nFrom 
