BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:7MA_yaouJom3HvbjkVuO9
SUMMARY:Silent Reading Night
DTSTAMP:20260308T063048Z
DTSTART:20260319T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Silent Reading Night – March Edition \\nDate: Thursday\\\, Marc
	h 19th \\nTime: 6:00 PM – 9:00 PM \\nTheme: Pages Shared: A Community Book
	 Exchange \\nWe wanted to celebrate this month’s silent reading night with
	 a community book exchange themed reading night! Feathered Pages will be t
	abling for this event. \\nEvent Activities: \\nCommunity Book Swap \\nTo p
	articipate in the book swap\\\, let the front desk know upon arrival and r
	eceive your raffle ticket. One book = 1 ticket. Feel free to bring as many
	 books as you would like to swap! \\n\\nGrab some wrapping paper from the 
	front desk with a blank note card that answers one of these two prompts:\\
	n“Why I loved this book…” or “describe this book in a sentence..”\\nWrap u
	p the book and tape the note card to the cover with the answered prompt.\\
	nDrop books at categorized area on the stage\\n\\n\\nFiction\\nNonfiction\
	\nRomance\\nFantasy/Sci-Fi\\nMemoir\\n\\nRaffle Announcement (at 8:30 PM) 
	\\nThere will be up to 5 winners! The prize is a Hugo House tote with book
	s inside! \\n \\nEvent Itinerary \\n6:00 PM – Mix & Mingle \\n\\nGrab a cu
	p of tea and settle in.\\nMeet fellow readers and share what book you’re c
	urrently enjoying.\\nBYOM – Bring Your Own Mug! Hot water will be availabl
	e.\\n\\n6:30 PM – Silent Reading Begins \\n\\nSettle into your cozy readin
	g spot and dive into your book.\\nEnjoy the quiet atmosphere of reading in
	 community.\\n\\n7:30 PM – Reading Break \\n\\nChat with your neighbor! As
	k them what they are reading.\\nGrab a snack or drink at the bar\\nCheck o
	ut Feathered Pages' book table\\n\\n7:40 PM – Break Ends \\n\\nHead back t
	o the Lapis Theater and do more reading.\\n\\n8:30 PM – Social Time & Book
	 Chats \\n\\nShare thoughts on your reads\\\, favorite passages\\\, or jus
	t connect with fellow book lovers.\\n3 raffle winners are announced.\\n\\n
	9:00 PM – Event Concludes \\n \\nThis is our monthly Silent Reading Night\
	\\, each month we will have a new theme to inspire your reading. Rediscove
	r the joy of reading in good company at the Hugo House. \\nWe can’t wait t
	o read with you!\n\nhttps://hugohouse.org/event/_2026-03-19/\n\nFrom Hugo 
	House
