SUMMARY:Gem Painting: Dazzling Book Covers Class at Swoon City
DTSTAMP:20260308T063048Z
DTSTART:20260326T173000Z
DESCRIPTION:In this delightful 2 hour workshop\\\, you’ll learn how place g
	em rhinestones on the cover of your favorite book to create a dazzling des
	ign sure to be the star of your shelfie. \\nOne note – you will likely NOT
	 COMPLETE a book cover in two hours but you will be able to do the letteri
	ng or other design elements. However you will take home up to gems and oth
	er supplies to finish your project at home\\\, if you choose. \\nYou can c
	hoose a book in the store which is valued $20 or less\\\, or you can bring
	 your own book\\\, and receive at $15 store credit. \\nAfter the workshop\
	\\, you’ll have all the skills you’ll need to continue your gem painting j
	ourney. No experience necessary\\\, beginners welcome. \\nThis class will 
	take place at Swoon City.\n\nhttps://myballard.com/event/gem-painting-dazz
	ling-book-covers-class-at-swoon-city/\n\nFrom My Ballard
