BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:P0rQl4UCtBcMLIOMpjscJ
SUMMARY:Print Class: Block Printing on Clothing
DTSTAMP:20260308T063048Z
DTSTART:20260328T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:Have a stain on your favorite shirt that you need to cover up? 
	Wanting to add a little extra flair to your favorite pair of jeans? Come l
	earn block printing basics and print onto your clothes with Alessia! \\nIn
	 this class you will learn the basics of block printing:\\n-creating a des
	ign\\n-carving your block\\n-inking and getting a clean print \\nPlease br
	ing your own garment(s) to print on and come prepared with an idea of what
	 you’d like to print! The blocks we’ll be using are 4”x 6” – feel free to 
	bring in a drawing or print-out and I’ll help you transfer it into your bl
	ock. Or come with just an idea and I’ll help you translate it into somethi
	ng printable! \\nUse our communal supplies in class\\\, or snag a block pr
	inting kit for 20% off if you buy it with your class ticket. \\nNote: Text
	ured fabrics like corduroy or knitted items are difficult to print on\\\, 
	please bring something that’s nice and smooth (i.e. cotton t-shirt\\\, den
	im\\\, etc.)\n\nhttps://myballard.com/event/print-class-block-printing-on-
	clothing/\n\nFrom My Ballard
URL:https://myballard.com/event/print-class-block-printing-on-clothing/
LOCATION:Swoon City\\\, 1716 NW Market St\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98107\\\, 
	United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:myballard
CATEGORIES:My Ballard
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
