UID:iiN2rkZTb860TrLLAuS9f
SUMMARY:Painting Class: Watercolor Landscapes for Beginners
DTSTAMP:20260308T063048Z
DTSTART:20260405T143000Z
DESCRIPTION:This step-by-step\\\, instructor-led watercolor class is design
	ed for beginners who want to learn how to paint beautiful landscapes with 
	confidence. No prior experience is needed. \\nYou’ll be guided through the
	 essential techniques used in watercolor landscape painting\\\, including:
	 \\nBasic and graded washes\\nComposition fundamentals\\nLayering to creat
	e depth and atmosphere\\nColor mixing for natural\\\, harmonious tones \\n
	With hands-on practice and individual guidance\\\, you will learn how to b
	uild a painting from start to finish and create your own completed landsca
	pe by the end of the session. \\nThe class is held in a relaxed and suppor
	tive environment\\\, making it a comfortable and encouraging space for tot
	al beginners. \\nAll materials and supplies are provided\\\, including a t
	ake-home watercolor kit (valued at $20) so you can continue practicing bey
	ond the classroom. \\nThis class will take place at Swoon City.\n\nhttps:/
	/myballard.com/event/painting-class-watercolor-landscapes-for-beginners/\n
	\nFrom My Ballard
URL:https://myballard.com/event/painting-class-watercolor-landscapes-for-be
	ginners/
